data.description: Location, Location, Location!! Just outside the city limits, this 3/2 is waiting for you. At nearly 2000 sq ft this home has generous bedrooms with walk-in closets, open family/kitchen area, kitchen pantry, lg laundry area and lots of storage. There is a screened in back deck for relaxing, 1 storage building and a 2 car carport. This one will not last long!!
